## ⚙️ Tech Stack

| Frontend             | Backend/API                  | Database       | Deployment |
|----------------------|------------------------------|----------------|------------|
| HTML, TailwindCSS, JS | Vercel Serverless (Node.js) | MongoDB Atlas  | Vercel     |

---

## 📝 Form Fields

- Full Name
- SAP ID (9 digits)
- Email Address
- Phone Number (10 digits)
- Preference 1, 2, 3 (team selection with dynamic filtering)
- Year of Study

---

## 🛠️ Local Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/CyberSentinel-UPES/Register-Page.git
cd Register-Page

# Create a .env file and add your Mongo URI
echo "MONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string" > .env

# Install dependencies (if applicable)
npm install
